OL,3,CGary McKee to run from from John o'
OL,4,CGroats to Land's End for hospitality
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FCumbrian 'Marathon Man' Gary McKee
OL,8,Fwill run the whole length of the UK,
OL,9,Fas part of a fundraiser for struggling
OL,10,Fhospitality workers.
OL,12,FGary, from Cleator Moor, has joined
OL,13,Fthe inaugural Licensed Trade Charity
OL,14,FJOGLE Pub Run 2026, and the charity is
OL,15,Faiming to raise #250,000 for people
OL,16,Ffacing difficulty across the licensed
OL,17,Fhospitality sector.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
