OL,3,CGary McKee to run from from John o'
OL,4,CGroats to Land's End for hospitality
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FGary said: "I've always believed that
OL,8,Fincredible things can happen when
OL,9,Fpeople come together behind a cause
OL,10,Fthat matters.
OL,12,F"The Licensed Trade Charity does vital
OL,13,Fwork supporting people throughout
OL,14,Fhospitality, and I'm proud to be part
OL,15,Fof a challenge that not only raises
OL,16,Ffunds but also shines a light on
OL,17,Fwellbeing, resilience and community
OL,18,Fspirit."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
