PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781626273
OL,3,CGary McKee to run from from John o'
OL,4,CGroats to Land's End for hospitality
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,FThe Pub Run will see participants take
OL,8,Fon a 900-mile relay journey from John
OL,9,Fo' Groats to Land's End over 30 days,
OL,10,Fbut Gary will run every stage of the
OL,11,Froute.
OL,13,FAs such, he will take part in
OL,14,Findividual legs, community days and
OL,15,Fvirtual challenges.
OL,17,FGary continued: "Running from John o'
OL,18,FGroats to Land's End is a huge
OL,19,Fchallenge, but the real motivation
OL,20,Fcomes from the people we'll meet along
OL,21,Fthe way.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781626273
OL,3,CGary McKee to run from from John o'
OL,4,CGroats to Land's End for hospitality
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,F"I hope my involvement encourages even
OL,8,Fmore individuals, teams and businesses
OL,9,Fto get behind the LTC JOGLE Pub Run
OL,10,Fand help make a lasting difference to
OL,11,Fthose working in an industry that is
OL,12,Fat the heart of so many
OL,14,FBritish communities."
OL,16,FJoby Mortimer, Director of Charity
OL,17,FOperations at the Licensed Trade
OL,18,FCharity, said: "We are absolutely
OL,19,Fthrilled to welcome Gary to the LTC
OL,20,FJOGLE Pub Run.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781626273
OL,3,CGary McKee to run from from John o'
OL,4,CGroats to Land's End for hospitality
OL,5,Cworkers
OL,7,F"His achievements speak for
OL,8,Fthemselves, but what makes Gary truly
OL,9,Fspecial is his ability to bring people
OL,10,Ftogether and inspire them to believe
OL,11,Fthey can achieve more than they
OL,12,Fthought possible."
OL,14,FThe challenge will take place between
OL,15,Fthe 13th July and 11th August.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
